Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,現在開始安排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,1號田中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,2號 捕球手 佐籐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,3號 擊球手 大島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,4號 2號壘 遠川
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,5號 佐籐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,（小泉日向）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.57,0:00:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我們最後的夏天開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,（棒球部女經紀人）\N（每天被用來性處理）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,（棒球部）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.27,0:01:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你起好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,早 這是最後-次比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道會如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是 不用這麼早起的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-你是第一的社員吧 -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.66,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大聲點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好好訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,用力揮棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,注意點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.01,0:03:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,用力點 手抬起來點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個該我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-辛苦了 -不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要寫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,-寫啊 -魂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:05:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是這個吧 -寫錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要鬧到甚麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,說了練習結束後馬上回去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-這個是甚麼\N-這個是小泉給大家準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-快點回去吧 -辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很生氣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:05:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,居然放過我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我收拾好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其實是關於一個學生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,他最近都很努力\N早上也是來最早的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是也該
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-不用 -但是\N-聽不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒事就回去吧 -告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,想著偶爾一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-感覺今天好累 -快死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,今天晚飯做甚麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-咖哩\N-真的嗎 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你很會做咖哩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我媽每次做咖哩\N都會問你要不要來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 回去以後要練習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-比起咖哩棒球更重要\N要練習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我們約好了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不得了 太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持這樣 也可以獲勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們不會這麼強\N-是啊 比起指導還是你更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-我們也是這樣覺得的\N-是啊 -安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,成績就算很好\N但我不讓和女人親熱的人上場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎麼了 有問題？\N-不 告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.53,0:11:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛你和他說的話\N是關於我的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜歡他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,經紀人跟隊員有感情\N對團隊發展不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,-我只是 -聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那個年齡的男生\N想到女生就不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才不要女經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你對他們態度不同 很爽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 我是喜歡棒球\N想和大家-起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不是為了那個男生嗎\N-我是為了團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為了團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不聽我話的人\N不覺得我為了團隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,求你讓他上場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想為了團隊是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那就該這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,給我含住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手甚麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想為了團隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為了這個才來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就做你該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.25,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快點 硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,給我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要對男人這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.52,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你也想對他這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好好握住肉棒 擼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:16:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,舌頭伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,給我舔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續舔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.98,0:17:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是你該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了嗎 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 快點舔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 就要改這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好好舔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,含住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,張開點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣 知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自己主動點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:19:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,手動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續深一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣男人才喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,來 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,靠著後面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.72,0:22:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,難受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.59,0:22:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,練習一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身體也要付出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要獻出身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有這麼輕霜的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.22,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.23,0:22:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那讓他無法參賽也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好軟的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有被揉過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你揉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-好色 -不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,興奮了嗎 乳頭硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.51,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.65,0:24:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,手放後面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,手敢放前面我就不讓他參賽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.29,0:25:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎 -不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.78,0:25:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.59,0:25:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.00,0:25:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,行了 張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.47,0:25:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.82,0:26:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.63,0:26:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,含住
